"uid":318474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"唔好嘗試自己清理受污染地區<br />\n<br />\n如果你只用水噴 D 罅及四周牆壁，D CS 同二噁英會俾你噴到周圍都係，自己由口鼻皮膚吸返。 <br />\n如果你用 1 分水 1 分甲醇(methanol)+哥士的(NaOH, KOH) 去水解 CS，D CS 會分解，但二噁英唔會。甲醇好易蒸發，你吸咗甲醇蒸氣，身體會將佢變成更加毒同嘅甲醛(methanal)，死快 D。<br />\n冇防毒衣同防化武豬咀，清潔唔到。"},{"pid":"559f9c8a19784876d33772a6bfa8f167960f7ceb","tid":1722952,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"支持 做人一定要有PR<br />\n<br />\n[星期六日行動post]商場和你唱唔等於嘉年華<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06146c8866bae8e04f79d0df7bbf12833a157bfb","tid":1722952,"uid":276821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"樓主呢個和你清潔幾好，支持搞"},{"pid":"1c060a2fa14c4f9d0df6f3569969caa610907ece","tid":1722952,"uid":326634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"喺條街度洗TG，其實都係變相堵路，由得民心又達到目的，但係唔知TG應該點洗."},{"pid":"77095743375aa6f7f6b21fe81dd32aa7f8d384a2","tid":1722952,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15948ce3a5323dc7c6d1c702178853a5fd198268","tid":1722952,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"阮文略 share嘅文章：<br />\n喺大家係咁share K Kwong既科學post時......我地向化學系同事請教左，佢話：CS 應該係創製者Corson 及 Stoughton 名字縮寫。按文章照做會害死人，甲醇好毒，特別對眼同肝。Decontamination唔係用甲醇，指引係用5% solution of sodium hydroxide in 50/50 ethyl alcohol/water去洗。詳見NIH的Toxnet。<br />\n不過無論點洗，始終有殘留，毒左傷左無得返轉頭🙈唔用方為上策<br />\n<br />\n（歡迎手動轉載唔洗問）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[純科學討論👷🏻&zwj;♀️]繼化學系同事糾正左有關TG decontamination既謬誤後，由我地既危險品管理同事分享吓，萬一落街食飯或屋企無辜辜中左招點算好：<br />\n(Assuming the TG used in HK contains mainly o-chlorobenzylidene malononitrile)<br />\n<br />\nCleaning / Neutralizing TG for common civilian / household: -<br />\n<br />\n1) Body - 3 rounds of cold shower. (NOT hot shower because heat activates TG)<br />\n<br />\n2) Eyes - Wash with water. Milk, or baking powder dissolved in water is even better.<br />\n<br />\n3) Clothing and bed sheets - discard<br />\n<br />\n4) Food - discard<br />\n<br />\n5) Air within home -  install air-purifier with HEPA-filter with charcoal odor- neutralizer<br />\n<br />\n6) Hard surfaces such as furniture - Scrub thoroughly with the following formulation:<br />\n<br />\n① 220 ml Isopropyl Alcohol  (一支 在藥房買到的 普通裝的 75% 外用酒精)<br />\n+<br />\n② 110 ml distilled water (e.g. 屈臣氏蒸餾水 )<br />\n+<br />\n③ 16 g Sodium Hydroxide (哥士的)<br />\n<br />\n（歡迎手動轉載唔洗問）"},{"pid":"c78f484e62bf28de4573a037e1d0acd0ad3e9746","tid":1722952,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1049c50f71ada0507f5ca7cf9f70f95ae05597a","tid":1722952,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15948ce3a5323dc7c6d1c702178853a5fd198268","tid":1722952,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"阮文略 share嘅文章：<br />\n喺大家係咁share K Kwong既科學post時......我地向化學系同事請教左，佢話：CS 應該係創製者Corson 及 Stoughton 名字縮寫。按文章照做會害死人，甲醇好毒，特別對眼同肝。Decontamination唔係用甲醇，指引係用5% solution of sodium hydroxide in 50/50 ethyl alcohol/water去洗。詳見NIH的Toxnet。<br />\n不過無論點洗，始終有殘留，毒左傷左無得返轉頭🙈唔用方為上策<br />\n<br />\n（歡迎手動轉載唔洗問）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&m